import React from "react";

function GrapesDecoration() {
  return (
    <svg
      width="143"
      height="266"
      viewBox="0 0 143 266"
      fill="none"
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      xmlnsXlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"
    >
      <rect width="143" height="266" fill="url(#pattern0)" />
      <defs>
        <pattern
          id="pattern0"
          patternContentUnits="objectBoundingBox"
          width="1"
          height="1"
        >
          <use
            xlinkHref="#image0_312_116"
            transform="matrix(0.00794932 0 0 0.0042735 -0.000806885 0)"
          />
        </pattern>
        <image
          id="image0_312_116"
          width="126"
          height="234"
          xlinkHref="data:image/png;base64,"
        />
      </defs>
    </svg>
  );
}

export default GrapesDecoration;
